OL,6,FA new law comes into force on
OL,7,FSaturday, 24 August making it a
OL,8,Fcriminal offence to steal a cat or a
OL,9,Fdog.
OL,11,FAnyone convicted of stealing them will
OL,12,Fface going to prison.
OL,14,FPreviously, the theft of much-loved
OL,15,Fpets would have been treated in the
OL,16,Fsame manner as a ball or garden tool
OL,17,Fbeing stolen ` inanimate objects.
OL,19,FBut there's a lot of money to be made
OL,20,Ffrom stealing dogs or cats, to order
OL,21,Fespecially pedigrees.
